               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1171" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1171" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1171" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1171" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WHITE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, R</hi> 180). On 7th March I was in the Broadway, at Deptford, between three and four o'clock—I saw, the two prisoners in company with another boy, who is not in custody—I watched them for about half an hour, over to Church-street, Greenwich, to Mr. Francis's shop—I saw the prisoners loiter about there for half an hour—I then saw Allen take a pair of trowsers, and give them to Lewis—I took the prisoners—Lewis threw the trowsers down, and said he had not got them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18490409-name-1172" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1172" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1172" type="surname" value="CARPENTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-1172" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN CARPENTER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, R</hi> 38). I was with White—I saw the prisoners—I watched them some time, but finding they knew me I got out of the way, got to the back of the shop, and ran round—I saw Lewis bringing this bundle under his arm—he turned back, ran away, and threw it into the gutter; it was this pair of trowsers, with a ticket of 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on them; they were inside the shop.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184904090192"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Lewis.</hi> I threw them down in the road, not in the gutter. <hi rend="smallCaps">JAMES FRANCIS</hi>. These are my property.</p>
